# --- operational scratch: NEVER commit (pre-publication sweep, 2026-07-20) ---
# These are local runbooks and generated logs that reference real infrastructure:
# SSH accounts (including a root login), the operator's private-key path, and the
# on-disk locations of live validator / miner signing SEEDS. The seeds themselves are
# already covered by `*.seed`, but a script that names where they live is nearly as
# useful to an attacker post-compromise. This repo is PUBLIC, so the gap is closed by
# pattern rather than by remembering.
*.log
kpq_*
scripts/utxoevm_*
scripts/palw-shared-testnet/env.local
